product_name: Keen Marshall WP Hiking Shoes - Women's
long_description: With breathable uppers and well-cushioned midsoles for all-day comfort, women's Keen Marshall Waterproof Hiking Shoes keep feet dry and provide a supportive platform for warm-weather hiking. Waterproof nylon mesh uppers with synthetic leather overlays provide lightweight structure and support while allowing cooling ventilation. KEEN.DRY(TM) waterproof, breathable membranes keep feet dry while allowing perspiration to dissipate. EVA footbeds deliver ample cushioning and are removable to accommodate orthotics. High-rebound polyurethane midsoles supply shock absorption for all-day comfort. Supportive thermoplastic urethane shanks enhance torsional stability on uneven terrain. Keen Marshall Waterproof Hiking Shoes for women have nonmarking rubber outsoles with 4mm multidirectional lugs for excellent all-around traction.
short_description: With breathable uppers and well-cushioned midsoles for all-day comfort, women's Keen Marshall Waterproof Hiking Shoes keep feet dry and provide a supportive platform for warm-weather hiking.
